{"tid":2208702,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"安倍晉三卸任首相僅3天　參拜靖國神社","createTime":"2020-09-19T06:26:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-19T07:50:38.000Z","uid":123774,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8c49586aa7ea0ef39d3ee357b8fc683543d69173","tid":2208702,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T06:26:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/abeshinzo/status/1307120105478934528?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fabeshinzo%2Fstatus%2F1307120105478934528%3Fs%3D21&d=QA0Qo2zDcB%2FuI%2B3HtJ%2FdClm6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=776d4f24\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fabeshinzo%2Fstatus%2F1307120105478934528%3Fs%3D21&h=fbce0dfb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/abeshinzo/status/1307120105478934528?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n靖國神社供奉緊被支那挑釁下<br />\n參與一場勢均力敵 旗鼓相當嘅紛爭嘅亡靈<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日本前首相安倍晉三早前因病辭職，周三（16日）在菅義偉就任後正式卸任。安倍卸任首相僅3天，今早（19日）他在Twitter發文及相片，表示已到過靖國神社參拜，向戰歿者報告自己卸任首相一事。<br />\n<br />\n安倍晉三2012年再次出任首相後，曾於2013年12月參拜供奉二戰甲級戰犯的靖國神社，是小泉純一郎之後再有在任首相參拜靖國神社。安倍此舉當時惹來中韓兩國嚴厲譴責，美國駐日使館亦罕有稱對安倍舉措「失望」。其後安倍再沒有參拜靖國神社，只以自民黨總裁名義獻上祭祀費。"},{"pid":"a563c75b460307695a46750895a472d208c80122","tid":2208702,"uid":57513,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T06:34:34.000Z","msg":"其實名冊成幾十萬人，定過百萬人，其中有11個係二戰甲級戰犯，講到好似得11個人咁。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dc07217d6358400df5592bca6bb94685a76972b","tid":2208702,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T07:50:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}